<2ND_LINE>PM-Wall Street 11am,0351</2ND_LINE>
<DATELINE>NEW YORK (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   The stock market was mixed in moderate trading
today as investors hesitated ahead of the release of important
economic data later in the week.
   The Dow Jones average of 30 industrials was unchanged at
2,095.99 in the first hour and a half of trading.
   Losers outnumbered gainers by about 3 to 2 in the overall tally
